# Ultrasonic Parking Sensor

## Objective
Build a parking assistance system using an HC-SR04 ultrasonic sensor.

## Components
- Arduino UNO
- HC-SR04
- LEDs
- Buzzer

## Working Principle
The ultrasonic sensor measures distance using sound waves.

Depending on the measured distance:
- Green LED indicates safe distance.
- Yellow LED indicates caution.
- Red LED and buzzer indicate immediate obstacle proximity.

## Concepts Used
- Ultrasonic sensing
- Pulse timing
- Conditional logic
- Embedded alert systems
